title: Leagrams Sunflower Heart Chips Wild Bird Food (25.1kg) - Husk Free and No Mess
features: Leagrams Quality: Trusted brand offering premium bird feeding solutions.
Sunflower heart chips provide the same nutrition as whole hearts, without birds having to waste energy breaking them open.
Perfect for smaller birds and fledglings, promoting healthy growth and development.
Packed with natural oils and high-energy nutrients to support bird health and vibrant feathers.
No mess, no waste – No discarded shells or husks, keeping your garden tidy.
Ideal for all types of feeders, including seed feeders, sunflower heart feeders, bird tables, and ground feeders.
description: Product description Leagrams Sunflower Heart Chips are premium, husk-free wild bird food, perfect for attracting a wide range of garden birds, including fledglings and smaller species. Packed with natural oils and essential nutrients, these sunflower chips provide a high-energy food source that supports healthy feathers, strong bones, and overall bird health. The no-mess, no-grow benefit eliminates discarded husks and prevents unwanted seed growth under your bird feeders, keeping your garden tidy and low-maintenance. Sourced from trusted European growers, these sunflower chips offer a clean, nutritious feeding option that is ideal for year-round bird feeding. Whether you use seed feeders, sunflower heart feeders, bird tables, or ground feeders, Leagrams husk-free sunflower chips are the perfect way to feed wild birds throughout all seasons, providing energy-rich food for wildlife, and supporting bird care all year long. Ingredients Sunflower Heart Chips Directions Use in a seed feeder or scatter on a bird table, and refill regularly to keep birds coming back. See more
